# TYPE (Issue) Brief summary (imperative mood, under 50 chars)

# Optional longer description (wrap at 72 chars)
# - Explain WHY this change is being made
# - Reference any related issues or context
# - Use bullet points for multiple items

# Issue Reference:
# - Use #123 for GitHub issues
# - Use PROJ-123 for external tracking systems
# - Use NA for commits without associated issues

# Commit Types:
# BREAK  - Breaking changes
# CI     - Changes in CI or docker files  
# DEPEN  - Changes in project dependencies
# DOCS   - Documentation changes
# ESLINT - Eslint/stylelint rule changes
# FEAT   - New feature
# FILES  - File/folder structure changes
# FIX    - Bug fixes
# FUNC   - Functionality changes to existing components
# STYLE  - Style file changes
# TEST   - Test additions/edits
# DB     - Database-related changes

# Examples:
# FEAT (#123) Add SMS support for Telnyx provider
# FIX (PROJ-456) Resolve authentication error
# DOCS (NA) Update API reference section
#
# - Implemented TelnyxSMSTransport class
# - Added authentication configuration
# - Included comprehensive unit tests
# - Updated documentation